    (date "2026-07-14")
    (rev "A0")
    (comment 1 "MCU, EMG, critical power, supervisor, RS-485, control IO")
  )
  (text "PCB-B_CTRL_RESERVE CONTAINS:\nMCU, watchdog/supervisor, EMG/KEEP_ALIVE, RESERVE_BRANCH, 5V_CRIT, 3V3_CRIT, isolated RS-485, optional CAN footprint DNP, service/debug, control and diagnostic IO."
    (at 20 25 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left))
  )
  (text "POWER RULES:\nReceives PACK_BUS_CRIT_IN only for critical/EMG path.\nDoes not carry summed CH1..CH14 current, 5V_SYS current, LED current, or BAT1/BAT2 main power.\n5V_CRIT and 3V3_CRIT do not power external outputs."
    (at 20 75 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left))
  )
  (text "SAFETY/CONTROL:\nEXT_KILL input must generate hardware final actions on PCB-A independent of MCU.\nMCU may log and supervise but must not be the only path for HARD_OFF.\nAll interboard signals follow Docs/INTERBOARD_INTERFACES.md and NET_NAMING_RULES.md."
    (at 20 135 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left))
  )
